    "causal_summary": "Phase 003 of the 118 FULL_ISOLATE_NO_MCP arc. Creates 4 .cjs script entry points (convergence/upsert/query/status) under .opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/ that replace the 4 deep_loop_graph_* MCP tools, and relocates deep-loop-graph.sqlite from MCP-server-managed storage into the runtime skill's storage/ directory. Scripts own DB lifecycle per invocation (open + close synchronously) — the canonical pattern from reduce-state.cjs. ADR-001 documents the choice with three rejected alternatives (shared daemon / MCP retains DB / file-based no-DB) and 5/5 Five Checks PASS. Single-owner invariant preserved by construction. Scaffolded; depends on phase 002 closeout; gates phase 004 (MCP handler removal).",
